Bug occurred for him on Win Chrome 3.0.195.38, occurs for me on mac FF 3.6.13, but *not* on Mac Safari 5.0.3.

Replacing resetSource() by setSource(null) does not work either. The only workaround I can think of is recreating a qx.ui.basic.Image from scratch
